text: #COVID19: @BorisJohnson welcomes new #vaccine @Novavax which has shown 89% efficacy in large-scale #UK trials. The PM says #UK’s medicines regulator will now assess the vaccine.The UK has secured 60 million doses of the jab which will be made in Stockton-on-Tees. #MHRA #Teesside https://t.co/RKe5FGDqTL
